<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%>
	   <a name=105139934325486></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f105139934325486><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=15&mid=105139934325486>RE: Stats</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=15&mid=105139934325486#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Scholar>Slipskin</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>787 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Apr 26th 8:01 PM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.64]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>From one Ogre Beastlord to another:<br><br>WIS is the stat I would choose. Ogres have fantastic starting STR and STA. No need to build those up. WIS is hurting. This means not enough mana to go around later on. <br><br>Before level 9 you shouldn't have any real issues in melee. Afterwards, in a straight stand up fight without your pet you are just begging for a dirt nap.&nbsp;&nbsp;So, you need your pet well buffed and yourself well buffed.  Unless, of course you group a lot.  I solo my BL entirely.<br><br>Point skill points into hand to hand mostly. Put 1 into sense heading and swim somewhere before 9 but not at level 1 or 2.  Piercing is OK but your epic is hand to hand. You can work on other weapons skills in your teens when you pet can do most of the damage output.<br><br>Skip conjuration until level 15. You don't get any spells in that category until then.<br><br>Do your Ogre BL armor quests. They are great for a long time.  The tunic is optional since you can buy better for under 35pp quite often in the bazaar.<br><br>Find someone to sell you some Polished Steel Ulaks for hand to hand weapons. They are very cheap.  I find them on vendors all the time for around 5pp.  Folks just sell them off as vendor trash.<br><br>DEX and AGI are weak on an Ogre BL.  Since they affect how fast you skill up on your offensive and defensive skills you might want to get some items to boost those over 80.  Otherwise it will take a lot longer to work those skills up.  Don't worry about maxing them right away. You will always level faster than your skills grow until around level 20.<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>

