	   <tr><td colspan=2>Contrary to common sense, it appears that you can give armor to your animal pet!&nbsp;&nbsp;I saw this on another messageboard and tried it out last evening while in Paludal.  Gave my pet a bunch of the Fungal armor drops and it made a HUGE difference in the pet's endurance.<br><br>Obviously the armor poofs with your pet when you zone so don't give him real expensive stuff :-)<br><br>I hear this works with weapons as well, but I didn't try it.<br><br>I'm sure someday this will get nerfed (since playing dress-up with your cat isn't very realistic), but for now I may just have found a use for all of that tailoring skill-up armor I'm making!<br><br>Just passing the word on.<br>&nbsp;<br>Heelem, Froglok Cleric<br>Squwaker, Vah Shir Beastmaster<br>Gilwedar, Woodelf Ranger<br><br>-- The Nameless --</td></tr>
