	   <tr><td colspan=2>Its not unusual to give pets armor and weapons.&nbsp;&nbsp;Necro's have been doing it for ages.  Make friends with a Magician that can summon NORENT armor and equip the pet. Or, like you, use the cheap stuff that you can afford to toss.  Also, if you get a cheap proc'ing weapon like Gnoll Hide Lariat (common drop in and around Splitpaw Lair) the pet will use the weapon and it will proc.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
