	   <tr><td colspan=2>Oh, and you want to concentrate on Hand to Hand, since your epic is Hand to Hand, and H2H is the only weapon skill Beastlords have that goes above 200 (it goes to 250) which will make a huge difference after level 50.&nbsp;&nbsp;I would also suggest trying to keep your Two Hand Blunt up, since it is handy to have a 2HB weapon for when you are fighting mobs with huge damage sheilds so you don't beat yourself to death with two fast weapons.  Not to mention there are some really amazing 2HB weapons out there (things with damage of 30 and delay of 20 for example), and if you do happen to have the chance to get one, it would be handy to have 2HB maxxed.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Sashaan Ahimsa<br>Esxaan Valdeeze<br>Kahlimaa Shivval<br>Sharlot Tradesmaster<br></td></tr>
